overview.en: Alatelecoin, a TOKEN based on ERC20, aimed to be the global open scale paid communication system. Within this system, user can directly connect each other and make value exchange like information, skills and property.
overview.zh: Alatelecoin(ATC)，中文夸克，是阿拉说旗下阿拉秀、学霸说及阿拉说APP通用的会员积分类ERC20 TOKEN，用户彼此之间通过ATC可轻松实现自由订单交易，比如服务、财物转移等，也可以通过ATC进入区块链生态，接入Defi、DAO、NFT等进行财务管理。
